{"tid":1528993,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"十萬火急!有份搞全球登報眾籌嘅巴絲可唔可以幫下手","createTime":"2019-09-01T15:47:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T11:33:50.000Z","uid":61876,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"40b2d8e5dd0fc9fedafcd345b51a66caae076b79","tid":1528993,"uid":61876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:47:47.000Z","msg":"咁事緣就係美國Florida 而家受五級颱風吹襲<br />\n當地人如臨大敵 就連特朗普都特登取消行程留守美國<br />\n咁呢個時候香港人如果好似以前捐錢返中國咁樣幫手賑災<br />\n就一定可以將呢個海外戰線擴展 爭取外國更加多人嘅支持<br />\n實現真正we connect<br />\n有啲人可能會話屌美國其實駛乜我哋幫<br />\n但其實我哋捐錢過去都係一份心意 冇理由要人哋幫手<br />\n但係係人哋美國人受天災影響嘅時候我哋唔出一份力<br />\n你要知道人禍係比起天災更加難應付<br />\n佢哋都願意幫助我哋對抗中共 咁我哋又點可以吝嗇自己嘅錢財？<br />\n至於你話點解要搵返之前眾籌班人呢<br />\n係因為佢哋有經驗同埋有公信力<br />\n由佢哋出嚟召集係可以更加有效果<br />\n所以希望你哋可以幫手 各位香港人亦都係呢啲時候幫下美國人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n光復香港時代革命"},{"pid":"d5ebf352f04d0c830bf2c9c74b611c866a75bcbd","tid":1528993,"uid":259345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:48:52.000Z","msg":"我忍左佢好撚耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一句講晒 聽日麻包袋藍絲副校長 割唔割<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1528684\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1528684</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"adeb60df28fa149b3e23011adbe63fd8f3cab0f1","tid":1528993,"uid":61876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:49:24.000Z","msg":"大力一推快啲We connect"},{"pid":"c1878037a4ee0e76838eee4a6fedc0c2b04f713f","tid":1528993,"uid":61876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,